title: Class 5A: Spring Lake Park defeats Park Center 28-22, returns to state tournament
text: Class 5A: Spring Lake Park remains undefeated, returns to state tournament 10/24/2015, 3:15pm CDT By David La Vaque, Star Tribune The top seed in Section 5 defeated Park Center 28-22, aided by four rushing touchdowns. Spring Lake Park running back Luke Stafford powered his way past Park Center defender Ryan Schnobrich en route to a touchdown in the first half of the game Saturday at Spring Lake Park.
